    <item>
      <title>美国货币市场基金创下 6.46 万亿美元历史新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/us-money-market-funds-hit-all-time-high-of-6-46-trillion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管美联储开始降息且一系列行业改革措施生效，但投资者仍大量涌入美国货币市场基金，推动该行业的总管理资产创下新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/us-money-market-funds-hit-all-time-high-of-6-46-trillion</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 20:07:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
